<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BGMI Registration - Clutch IIIT Kota</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Funnel+Display:wght@300..800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/media/clutch logo circle.png">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
            cursor: default;
        }

        html,
        body {
            min-height: 100%;
            font-family: "Funnel Display", sans-serif;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .hero_section {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: flex-start;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .hero_section .video_filter {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: black;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        .hero_section video {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .navbar {
            position: fixed;
            height: 50px;
            width: 95%;
            top: 20px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            border-radius: 42px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2) 100%);
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .logo {
            aspect-ratio: 1;
            object-fit: contain;
            object-position: center;
            width: 38px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .navbar-left {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 14px;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: "Funnel Display";
            font-size: 22px;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: normal;
            letter-spacing: -0.96px;
            position: relative;
            left: 10px;
        }

        .navbar-right {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 30px;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: "Funnel Display";
            font-size: 20px;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 500;
            position: relative;
            right: 20px;
        }

        a.nav-link {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: flex-start;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 120px 40px 50px;
            gap: 40px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            max-width: 1400px;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .form-section {
            background: rgba(40, 40, 40, 0.95);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 40px;
            flex: 1;
            max-width: 50vw;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            margin-right: 300px;
        }

        .game-info {
            background: rgba(40, 40, 40, 0.95);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            width: 25vw;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            height: fit-content;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            position: fixed;
            top: 120px;
            right: 100px;
        }

        .game-info img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff4655 0%, #ff6b75 100%);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .bgmi-placeholder {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff4655 0%, #ff6b75 100%);
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .game-info h2 {
            color: #ff003c;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .game-info ul {
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #ccc;
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .game-info li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 15px;
        }

        .game-info li:before {
            content: "â€¢";
            color: #ff003c;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #ff003c;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .team-section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .team-section h3 {
            color: white;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            color: #ccc;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .form-group input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            background: rgba(60, 60, 60, 0.8);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 8px;
            color: white;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: border-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .form-group input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #ff003c;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 0, 60, 0.3);
        }

        .form-group input::placeholder {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }

        .player-section {
            background: rgba(50, 50, 50, 0.6);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 0, 60, 0.2);
        }

        .player-section h4 {
            color: #ff003c;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .submit-btn {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff003c 0%, #cc0030 100%);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            color: white;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .submit-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 0, 60, 0.4);
        }

        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .container {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                padding: 120px 20px 50px;
            }

            .game-info {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 800px;
                order: -1;
                position: static;
            }

            .form-section {
                width: 100%;
                background: rgba(40, 40, 40, 0.95);
                border-radius: 15px;
                padding: 40px;
                flex: 1;
                max-width: 800px;
                box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
                backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
                margin-right: 0;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .navbar-left {
                font-size: 16px;
                gap: 10px;
            }

            .navbar-right {
                font-size: 15px;
                gap: 20px;
            }

            .container {
                padding: 100px 15px 30px;
            }

            .form-section,
            .game-info {
                padding: 25px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="hero_section">
        <video autoplay loop muted>
            <source src="/media/clutch website bg glitch.mp4" type="video/mp4">
            Your browser does not support the video tag.
        </video>
        <div class="video_filter"></div>

        <nav class="navbar">
            <div class="navbar-left">
                <img src="/media/clutch logo circle.png" class="logo" alt="Clutch logo">
                <a href="/" class="nav-link">our network</a>
            </div>
            <div class="navbar-right">
                <a href="/#tournaments" class="nav-link">tournaments</a>
                <a href="/#contact" class="nav-link">contact us</a>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <div class="container">
            <div class="form-section">
                <h1>Enter your Team details</h1>

                <form id="bgmiForm" action="/register/bgmi/submit" method="POST">
                    <div class="team-section">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="teamName">Team name</label>
                            <input type="text" id="teamName" name="teamName" placeholder="Enter team name" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="contactNumber">Contact Number</label>
                            <input type="tel" id="contactNumber" name="contactNumber" placeholder="Enter contact number"
                                required>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="player-section">
                        <h4>Player 1 details (IGL)</h4>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="player1Name">Name</label>
                            <input type="text" id="player1Name" name="player1Name" placeholder="Enter player name"
                                required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="player1IGN">IGN</label>
                            <input type="text" id="player1IGN" name="player1IGN" placeholder="Enter In Game Name"
                                required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="player1UID">UID</label>
                            <input type="text" id="player1UID" name="player1UID" placeholder="Enter UID"
                                required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="player1Email">Email</label>
                            <input type="email" id="player1Email" name="player1Email" placeholder="Enter email"
                                required>
                        </div>
                        
                    </div>

                    <div class="player-section">
                        <h4>Player 2</h4>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="player2Name">Name</label>
                            <input type="text" id="player2Name" name="player2Name" placeholder="Enter player name"
                                required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="player2IGN">IGN</label>
                            <input type="text" id="player2IGN" name="player2IGN" placeholder="Enter In Game Name"
                                required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="player2UID">UID</label>
                            <input type="text" id="player2UID" name="player2UID" placeholder="Enter UID" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="player2Email">Email</label>
                            <input type="email" id="player2Email" name="player2Email" placeholder="Enter email"
                                required>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="player-section">
                        <h4>Player 3</h4>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="player3Name">Name</label>
                            <input type="text" id="player3Name" name="player3Name" placeholder="Enter player name"
                                required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="player3IGN">IGN</label>
                            <input type="text" id="player3IGN" name="player3IGN" placeholder="Enter In Game Name"
                                required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="player3UID">UID</label>
                            <input type="text" id="player3UID" name="player3UID" placeholder="Enter UID" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="player3Email">Email</label>
                            <input type="email" id="player3Email" name="player3Email" placeholder="Enter email"
                                required>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="player-section">
                        <h4>Player 4</h4>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="player4Name">Name</label>
                            <input type="text" id="player4Name" name="player4Name" placeholder="Enter player name"
                                required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="player4IGN">IGN</label>
                            <input type="text" id="player4IGN" name="player4IGN" placeholder="Enter In Game Name"
                                required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="player4UID">UID</label>
                            <input type="text" id="player4UID" name="player4UID" placeholder="Enter UID" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="player4Email">Email</label>
                            <input type="email" id="player4Email" name="player4Email" placeholder="Enter email"
                                required>
                        </div>
                    </div>


                    <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Register Team</button>
                </form>
            </div>

            <div class="game-info">
                <div class="bgmi-placeholder" style="background-image: url('/media/bgmi.jpg')">
                </div>
                <h2>BGMI Registration</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>4 players are allowed</li>
                    <li>Only IIIT Kota students are allowed to play in the tournament</li>
                    <li>Only Team leader needs to register the team</li>
                    <li>Use college email for registration</li>
                    <li>Players must play with the IDs specified during registration</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>